# 82. PSA Scenario – Payment Failure Analysis

Suppose a transaction file contains:

```text
2026-07-08 TXN1001 SUCCESS 5000
2026-07-08 TXN1002 FAILED 3000
2026-07-08 TXN1003 FAILED 7000
2026-07-08 TXN1004 SUCCESS 2500
```

